uk.ac.ebi.kraken.interfaces.uniprot.features

Interface CarbohydFeature

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Feature, HasEvidences, HasFeatureDescription, HasFeatureId, HasFeatureStatus, Serializable

    public interface CarbohydFeature
extends Feature, HasFeatureDescription, HasFeatureId
    Encapsulates the CarbohydFeature of a UniProtEntry.

    These values can be found in the FT CARBOHYD line of the flat file on the marked position. 
    
 FT   TOPO_DOM     26    371       Lumenal (Potential).
 
    
 FT   CARBOHYD    143    143       N-linked (GlcNAc...) (Potential).
 FT   VARIANT     344    344       G -> W (in strain BLG2/Msf).
 SQ   SEQUENCE   371 AA;  41236 MW;  323A7FFA56B723B3 CRC64;
 ...
